The gun is in overall good shape no pitting or rust but it does have dings and scratches in the metal. The wood is in good + shape with good original finish and a few minor dings and scratches.  Functions flawlessly execllent shooter. The only downfall to the gun is it has been rechambered in 357mag. It sucks i know but it has... it had the barrel and the chamber rebored.
